00:00:02.188 --> 00:00:06.147
THIS IS TAPE SEVEN OF AN INTERVIEW WITH LEE SHULDMAN,

00:00:06.289 --> 00:00:09.995
JUNE EIGHTH, NINETEEN NINETY-EIGHT, IN BROOKLYN, NEW YORK.

00:00:11.804 --> 00:00:15.727
eyder mir g- on- mir geyen on vayter, muz ikh bay aykh fregn:

00:00:15.727 --> 00:00:19.588
 di S.S.kes, di S.S., f-,

00:00:19.588 --> 00:00:25.677
mentshn hobn aykh gelozt. ver hot ay- ibergenumen aykh tsu⟨m⟩ firn? andere S.S.n?

00:00:22.810 --> 00:00:28.147
andere. andere S.S., ye, andere S.S., ye. un kapos oykhet.

00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:27.562
un,

00:00:28.125 --> 00:00:31.291
mit kapos oy- oykhet, mit yidishe kapos?

00:00:28.147 --> 00:00:30.501
S.S. mit kapos, ye.

00:00:30.501 --> 00:00:36.408
NO, NO. s'iz dortn geven a gemish. me ken nit, s'iz geven a gemish: polkes, poyl-, farshidene.

00:00:36.408 --> 00:00:38.261
ken nit zogn velkhe EXACTLY.

00:00:37.997 --> 00:00:42.783
un di, di gefangene vos ir hot gezen, zaynen zey ale geven yidn?

00:00:42.992 --> 00:00:44.572
in velkhe, di,...?

00:00:43.819 --> 00:00:45.264
in ⟨d-⟩ in,

00:00:45.270 --> 00:00:46.732
in BERGEN-BELSEN,

00:00:46.958 --> 00:00:48.049
tsvishn...

00:00:47.076 --> 00:00:53.421
NO, s'iz geven farshidene. in Bergen-Belzen ⟨iz⟩ geven farshidene NATION- ⟨natsyonalitet⟩.

00:00:53.421 --> 00:00:54.801
s'iz geven farshidene.

00:00:54.801 --> 00:00:55.895
s'iz g- ye.

00:00:56.610 --> 00:01:00.148
hot ir gezen, tsum bayshpil, vos far a natsyonalitetn?

00:00:59.074 --> 00:01:02.865
NO. ver hot gevust? ver hot ge- ⟨⟩...?

00:01:03.040 --> 00:01:04.434
⟨, m'hot z-...⟩

00:01:04.456 --> 00:01:07.955
 m'hot undz dan aribergenumen tsu di froyen-lagers.

00:01:07.955 --> 00:01:09.632
iz in dem TSRIF

00:01:09.925 --> 00:01:11.845
zaynen dortn nokh geven

00:01:11.845 --> 00:01:13.124
etlekhe f-

00:01:13.253 --> 00:01:14.537
meydlekh,

00:01:14.537 --> 00:01:15.538
froyen.

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:19.048
hot men aroysgeshlept di froyen,

00:01:19.408 --> 00:01:21.404
mit vundn oyfn...

00:01:21.404 --> 00:01:24.678
hobn zey gehat, un m'hot zey aroysgeshlept lebedikerheyt

00:01:24.678 --> 00:01:32.733
un aroyfgevorfn oykh dortn vu s'iz gelegn di toyte. dortn iz oykh gelegn a, a, a, a hoyfn mit toyte, froyen.

00:01:32.925 --> 00:01:37.858
un zey hobn azoy gekrekhtset. m'hot zey geshlept oyf dr'erd, hot dos geribn nokh mer.

00:01:37.858 --> 00:01:39.838
un zey zaynen nokh lebedik geven.

00:01:40.013 --> 00:01:46.386
un m'hot zey aroysgeshlept fun barak, un m'hot zey aroyfgevorfn oyf di toyte dortn, vos iz geven lem barak.

00:01:46.577 --> 00:01:50.283
nakher hot men undz arayngelozn, di finf hundert froyen,

00:01:50.340 --> 00:01:52.919
un m'iz gezesn a gantse nakht azoy,

00:01:52.919 --> 00:02:01.007
eyner tsum andern tsugerukt mit di kni, vayle finf hundert froyen, iz dokh nit geven keyn plats zikh tsu, ⟨⟩,

00:02:01.007 --> 00:02:02.484
oystsien a fus.

00:02:02.659 --> 00:02:05.201
un azoy iz men opgelegn a nakht.

00:02:05.562 --> 00:02:09.828
kh'veys nit vos hot pasirt. oyf morgn hot men gemakht far undz

00:02:09.828 --> 00:02:10.786
pritshn,

00:02:11.198 --> 00:02:12.036
betn.

00:02:13.054 --> 00:02:19.697
tsi zey hobn shoyn gevust az s'iz shoyn nont efsher ts- ende tsu di krig oder vos... zey hobn dokh gevust, di daytshn.

00:02:19.737 --> 00:02:25.063
hobn zey efsher gevelt vayzn az m- m- me ligt vi mentshn oder vos.

00:02:25.170 --> 00:02:30.513
un dortn iz geven a lager oykh nor tsum shtarbn, vayle arbetn hot men nit gearbet

00:02:30.756 --> 00:02:32.069
un esn

00:02:32.069 --> 00:02:35.906
hot men gegebn ⟨abi⟩... ershtns, iz nit geven in vos tsum esn,

00:02:35.906 --> 00:02:42.090
nor m'hot oyfgeklibn fun droysn vos s'iz geblibn fun a toytn oder vos: a tepele, a shisele.

00:02:42.653 --> 00:02:46.882
iz ver s'hot gehat hot gehat un ver s'hot nit ge- m'hot nit gegebn keyn geshir.

00:02:47.395 --> 00:02:52.147
un me hot g- in der fri hot men gegebn a bisl vaser azoy, ⟨es⟩ heyst a "tey."

00:02:52.626 --> 00:02:56.096
iz ver s'hot gekrogn hot gekrogn; ver s'hot nit gekrogn hot nit gekrogn.

00:02:56.119 --> 00:03:01.587
un bay tog hot men gebrakht a bisl fun, farmisht fun mel aza zup.

00:03:01.587 --> 00:03:03.893
iz oykh nit ale hobn gehat, gekrogn.

00:03:03.713 --> 00:03:10.592
vo- vos iz geven di shtimungen in der nakht ven ir hot gevart un gezen vifl, vos far a, vos f-...?

00:03:09.383 --> 00:03:15.857
 biter oyfn hartsn iz geven. m'hot gezen, ALRIGHT, m'iz geven in Hamburg, hot men nit gezen di toyte,

00:03:15.930 --> 00:03:17.054
azoy fil.

00:03:17.112 --> 00:03:25.020
in der, in Estland, ⟨, s'⟩iz geshtorbn, oder m'hot derharget, oder s'iz nit gelegn gantse berg. gantse berg mit toyte iz gelegn.

00:03:25.245 --> 00:03:29.053
gantse berg. eyner oyf di andere, eyner oyf di andere toyte.

00:03:29.177 --> 00:03:30.321
m'hot dos derzen,

00:03:29.260 --> 00:03:29.695
⟨...⟩

00:03:30.321 --> 00:03:31.494
hot men gevust

00:03:31.494 --> 00:03:33.747
az mir'n oykhet do shtarbn shoyn,

00:03:33.747 --> 00:03:34.951
un,

00:03:35.033 --> 00:03:40.595
un, zeyer a shlekhte shtimung iz geven, ober vos hot men gekent ton? m'hot dokh gornit gekent ton.

00:03:40.348 --> 00:03:42.924
keyner iz nisht gevorn histerish?

00:03:43.605 --> 00:03:47.750
NO. ir zet, in Shtuthof iz gevorn histerish, gedenk ikh,

00:03:47.925 --> 00:03:50.638
a, iz gekumen a doktershe mit a dokter.

00:03:50.638 --> 00:03:56.559
hobn zey gehat PILLS un zey hobn bald genumen PILLS un zaynen ayngeshlofn. zey hobn zikh tsugegreyt, ye.

00:03:56.599 --> 00:04:00.521
histerish. m'hot geveynt, m'hot ger- ober m'hot dokh gornit gekent ton.

00:04:00.521 --> 00:04:08.000
vos,...? me volt nor gezen az me shrayt oder me veynt, volt men gekhapt mit a, fun di, fun di daytshn a klap, fun di kapos.

00:04:08.344 --> 00:04:09.097
ye.

00:04:09.053 --> 00:04:14.717
me, m'hot geredt tsvishn aykh un gemakht a, me, m'hot getrofn vos vet z- zayn der sof?

00:04:09.289 --> 00:04:10.042
s-

00:04:11.027 --> 00:04:12.133
tsevish-...

00:04:14.098 --> 00:04:21.432
m'hot geredt tsevishn zikh, SURE, avade. m'hot gezen, un m'hot, me, me, me, m'hot nit gedarft reydn; m'hot gezen vos vet zayn tsu undz.

00:04:20.629 --> 00:04:23.728
un vos, vos hot ir getrakht? vos hot ir gezogt?

00:04:22.637 --> 00:04:25.165
m'hot getrakht, "nu, vos ken men shoyn ton?"

00:04:25.165 --> 00:04:29.196
UNK dos iz der goyrl." un m'hot getrakht az,

00:04:29.438 --> 00:04:31.308
m- mir kenen zikh nit helfn.

00:04:31.308 --> 00:04:36.316
frier eyner vet geyn, oder shpeter, ⟨az s'⟩ iz gelegn azoyne berg mit mentshn.

00:04:36.373 --> 00:04:38.792
ong- berg mit mentshn.

00:04:38.792 --> 00:04:43.134
un der lager-firer hot geheysn, dakht zikh, KRAMER, gedenk ikh vi hay-... un s'iz geven

00:04:43.208 --> 00:04:47.246
a daytshke, a hoykhe, a l- a, a l- a lager-firerke. ir nomen gede-...

00:04:47.246 --> 00:04:54.677
nor ⟨p-⟩ antis- vos heyst, m'hot moyre gehat vi far fayer far zey. far fayer hot men gornit azoy moyre vi far zey.

00:04:54.953 --> 00:04:55.979
iz,

00:04:55.979 --> 00:04:58.001
m'hot undz gemakht di pritshn.

00:04:58.007 --> 00:05:00.549
nu, iz men shoyn gelegn oyf di pritshn.

00:05:01.298 --> 00:05:04.144
in eyn tog iz gekumen epes a daytsh

00:05:04.352 --> 00:05:10.978
un hot oysgeklibn bay undz, fun di finf hundert froyen, tsen meydlekh, in kikh tsu sh- trogn vaser

00:05:11.170 --> 00:05:12.432
in kikh arayn.

00:05:12.432 --> 00:05:15.248
un di kikh iz geven oyfn zayt fun di mener.

00:05:16.401 --> 00:05:19.584
flegt er kumen ale inderfri nemen di tsen froyen.

00:05:19.675 --> 00:05:22.166
un ikh bin geven tsevishn di tsen froyen.

00:05:22.543 --> 00:05:26.671
zet oyset az mayn mame ober got hot zikh far mir gemit.

00:05:27.387 --> 00:05:30.395
epes hot pasirt az ikh...

00:05:30.395 --> 00:05:35.481
epes. zet oys, kh'hob geton guts oykhet. kh'hob gegebn ⟨v- az⟩ ikh hob gehat, hob ikh avekgegebn.

00:05:37.495 --> 00:05:39.643
un ikh bin dortn gegangen.

00:05:39.643 --> 00:05:41.977
iz geven a baseyn

00:05:42.220 --> 00:05:46.382
mit vaser, un m'hot getrogn fun dem baseyn in kikh arayn

00:05:46.962 --> 00:05:55.596
tsu, tsu makhn di keslekh mit vaser. un m'hot dos gekokht mit a bisl mel farmisht tsu makhn zup far di mentshn in lager.

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:58.864
s'hobn gekro-, dortn iz geven toyznter mentshn,

00:05:58.864 --> 00:06:02.194
un efsher hobn gekrogn hundert mentshn e- esn.

00:06:02.368 --> 00:06:08.892
un, kartofl hot men oykhet, iz geven a ⟨sheyl-kikh⟩ dortn, hot men dos alts geton.

00:06:10.840 --> 00:06:19.373
in eyn, un in, un ven mir hobn gehat di nares, hot azoy bombardirt un azoy geshosn, az mir zaynen aropgefaln fun di nares. ⟨s-⟩

00:06:19.373 --> 00:06:21.566
zet oys, m'hot gesho- bombardirt.

00:06:22.585 --> 00:06:23.456
in,

00:06:23.918 --> 00:06:25.903
in,

00:06:26.584 --> 00:06:29.902
eyn mol shtey ikh azoy un ikh shlep di vaser,

00:06:31.782 --> 00:06:36.900
un di daytshke shteyt dortn mit aza rut un zi shmayst: "shneler, shneler!"

00:06:36.900 --> 00:06:39.811
un nit ikh aleyn; nokh a meydl iz oykh gegangen.

00:06:39.814 --> 00:06:41.718
mit a mol, derze ikh

00:06:41.718 --> 00:06:43.453
a hoykher man...

00:06:44.370 --> 00:06:48.932
yetst farshtey ikh, un nakher hob ikh, nokh di bafrayung, az s'iz geven a tankist,

00:06:48.932 --> 00:06:50.220
fun di tanken,

00:06:50.361 --> 00:06:54.804
un er iz geven an Englender, ober dan hot men nit gevust ver er iz un vos er iz.

00:06:54.647 --> 00:06:56.126
vi hot er oysgezen?

00:06:54.804 --> 00:06:55.772
nu, a man...

00:06:55.980 --> 00:07:02.454
a hoykher, an ander UNIFORM vi di daytshn, mit aza, oyfn kop getrogn aza hut, a⟨z-⟩...

00:07:02.629 --> 00:07:04.356
ye. shpeter hot men g-

00:07:03.321 --> 00:07:04.884
aza HELMET?

00:07:04.705 --> 00:07:07.646
e- epes aza, vi fun di tanken.

00:07:07.646 --> 00:07:14.199
y- shpeter, ober ven er iz gegangen, hot men gezen aza hoy- ⟨un⟩ er iz aroyf dortn bizn KREMATORIUM.

00:07:14.593 --> 00:07:18.451
nakher iz er gegangen tsurik, un er hot gezen az di daytshke

00:07:18.458 --> 00:07:23.227
shmayst mitn rut, iz er tsu tsu ir, un geheysn ir avekleygn di rut.

00:07:23.892 --> 00:07:28.611
azoy vi er hot ir geheysn di rut avekleygn, hot genumen arbetn di kop:

00:07:28.785 --> 00:07:31.513
"vos kumt do for? vos iz do?"

00:07:32.430 --> 00:07:38.409
a daytsh vet dokh nit heysn avekleygn di rut. hot men genu- un me zet dokh epes, er geyt onget- az s'iz nit a daytshisher.

00:07:38.409 --> 00:07:41.503
ober m'hot alts nit gevust vos do kumt for.

00:07:42.538 --> 00:07:46.379
mit eyn mol... iz dos geven mistome a zeyger elf-tsvelf.

00:07:46.909 --> 00:07:47.910
dos iz,

00:07:47.910 --> 00:07:49.923
 APRIL ⟨THE⟩ fuftsn.

00:07:51.297 --> 00:07:55.520
un ale daytshn fun oybn, vos zaynen gezesn

00:07:55.520 --> 00:07:59.103
oyf di budke⟨s⟩ vu zey flegn oybn hitn un shisn arop,

00:07:59.515 --> 00:08:04.824
un di fun kikh, di daytshn, un dortn nokh daytshn vos hobn zikh, gedreyt...

00:08:05.623 --> 00:08:11.000
hot men farmakht di kikh. di keslekh hobn gekokht, vayle s'iz dokh geven nokh...

00:08:12.036 --> 00:08:15.101
un zaynen ale mit a mol avek.

00:08:15.431 --> 00:08:24.366
az s'zaynen ale avek mit a mol, hot men vayter genumen klern: "vos kumt do for? epes kumt do for, oder mir veysn nit vos es kumt for."

00:08:23.933 --> 00:08:25.867
de- der Englender iz avek?

00:08:25.941 --> 00:08:27.960
NO, di daytshn, di daytshn.

00:08:26.852 --> 00:08:30.153
oh, der, der, der Englender iz geblibn do mit aykh?

00:08:29.603 --> 00:08:33.329
NO, NO. der man iz avek tsum lager, un avek tsurik.

00:08:30.767 --> 00:08:32.415
er iz farbaygegangen.

00:08:33.329 --> 00:08:38.810
zet oys az zey zaynen geven dortn bayn toyer fun lager, fun, fun onheyb lager.

00:08:39.087 --> 00:08:44.616
un, d- dortn iz geshtanen di komendantur oykh, di daytshishe gantse firershaft.

00:08:44.824 --> 00:08:53.272
un di ale daytshn, alts avek. der lager iz toy- nit oybn keyn gever mit daytshn, nit in kikh NOBODY; farhakt, farmakht.

00:08:53.481 --> 00:08:57.072
di mener zaynen geven antkegn, hinter drotn,

00:08:57.072 --> 00:09:00.191
un lem kikh iz gelegn ongeshotn kartofl

00:09:00.568 --> 00:09:02.553
tsum sheyln, tsum kikh.

00:09:02.982 --> 00:09:07.639
di mener hobn derzen az keyner ⟨iz⟩ nito, oder vos un ven v-, veys men nit.

00:09:08.162 --> 00:09:09.382
zaynen zey

00:09:09.382 --> 00:09:18.782
aroysgeshtupt dem toyer, dem, dem, d⟨i⟩ hiltsernem toyer, un aroyfgelofn oyf di kartofl, khapn a kartofl; zaynen dokh hungerik ale geven.

00:09:18.782 --> 00:09:22.314
hungerik! dortn i- iz geven a lager tsum shtarbn.

00:09:24.193 --> 00:09:27.967
efsher in a halbe sho a-, hot genumen,

00:09:28.699 --> 00:09:33.772
hostu gezen: oyf ferd zaynen gekumen tsurik di daytshn mit vayse lentes

00:09:34.403 --> 00:09:39.729
un aroyfgelofn oybn tsu di gever un genumen shisn

00:09:40.292 --> 00:09:43.593
oyf di mener vos zaynen gelegn oyf di kartofl.

00:09:43.701 --> 00:09:48.302
un bay undz iz arayngelofn der daytsh fun kikh mit a revolver in hant.

00:09:48.460 --> 00:09:50.279
"mener, mener!" hot er gezukht.

00:09:50.279 --> 00:09:55.246
mir hobn aleyn geshtanen, hot undz gevorfn; zey kenen dokh undz oykh shi- se shpilt a, a, me,...

00:09:56.121 --> 00:09:59.507
un oysgeshosn a por sheyne y- mener.

00:10:01.707 --> 00:10:06.071
in, efsher in a fuftsn-tsvantsik minut arum

00:10:06.145 --> 00:10:08.619
iz geforn a tank, take

00:10:08.642 --> 00:10:11.994
a tank azoy vi der man vos iz geforn,

00:10:12.338 --> 00:10:16.350
un in ale shprakhn gezogt az mir zaynen bafrayt.

00:10:16.928 --> 00:10:22.792
in yidish, in poylish, in rusish, in ale shprakhn: mir zaynen bafrayt.

00:10:23.290 --> 00:10:30.878
iz, shtelt zikh for: m'iz shoyn geven bafrayt, vayl zey zaynen geshtanen bayn toyer, un der tankist iz dokh geven in lager,

00:10:31.052 --> 00:10:35.311
un di daytshn hobn dokh shoyn getrogn lentes. zey hobn zikh dokh shoyn untergegebn, zet ⟨oy-⟩

00:10:35.311 --> 00:10:40.546
un zaynen gekumen tsurik un di mener geshosn. dos iz shoyn geven efsher a sho

00:10:40.587 --> 00:10:44.110
vi der tank hot shoyn gezogt az mir zaynen bafrayt, ober bafrayt

00:10:44.110 --> 00:10:48.194
zayne- iz men dokh shoyn geven, vayl der Englender ⟨iz dokh⟩ geshtanen bayn toyer fornt.

00:10:48.194 --> 00:10:50.430
hot men oysgeshosn azoy

00:10:50.430 --> 00:10:52.190
sheyne por mener

00:10:52.433 --> 00:10:54.802
vos zaynen gelegn oyf di kartofl.

00:10:55.555 --> 00:11:00.799
un nakher, nu, nakher iz dokh gevorn a ⟨he-⟩ a, hot men di daytshn

00:11:00.799 --> 00:11:02.399
ale tsugenumen.

00:11:02.490 --> 00:11:04.509
un ikh gedenk nokh vi haynt

00:11:04.583 --> 00:11:11.951
vi s'iz gegangen vayter nokh a, oykhet a militer-man mit dem lager-firer, KRAMER hot er...

00:11:11.974 --> 00:11:13.489
un tsum

00:11:13.489 --> 00:11:18.923
gaz-kamer, un nakher tsurik, un nakher hobn mir gezen vi er hot im aropgenumen dem zeyger,

00:11:18.923 --> 00:11:22.954
un aropgenumen dortn zayne epoletn, vosEVER er hot gehat,

00:11:22.977 --> 00:11:27.780
un m'hot im arestirt., dakht zikh az me hot im derharget, oder mir veysn nit.

00:11:27.820 --> 00:11:30.331
un di daytshkes vos UNK zayn,

00:11:30.331 --> 00:11:39.102
hobn mir gevelt ale fun zey aropraysn di shtivl tsu nemen, ontsuton far undz, oder epes... di Englender hobn undz nit tsugelozn tsu zey.

00:11:39.102 --> 00:11:43.828
zey hobn undz nit tsugelozn. zey hobn zey azoy gehit; zey hobn... me hot zey gevelt tseraysn, obe-...

00:11:44.307 --> 00:11:46.883
nakhe-, dos iz geven in lager,

00:11:46.905 --> 00:11:52.029
un mentshn zaynen geshtorbn. far vos? m'iz geven mitn TYPHUS krank.

00:11:52.542 --> 00:12:04.703
un az me hot geefnt dortn di k- di skladn, vu s'iz geven broyt mit tsuker mit esn, vos m'hot undz nit gegebn... s'iz efsher geven far di daytshn oder s'iz geven efsher far di, fa- ikh veys nit...

00:12:04.843 --> 00:12:10.490
hot men genumen khapn un esn, ober m'hot dos nit getort, vayle m'iz geven

00:12:10.733 --> 00:12:14.239
oysgedart, nit gegesn, iz der mogn geven,

00:12:14.239 --> 00:12:16.363
 zeyer DELICATE.

00:12:16.605 --> 00:12:20.354
iz a sakh mentshn zaynen geshtorbn nokh di bafrayung.

00:12:19.205 --> 00:12:24.149
fun aykh, fun di finef hundert meydlekh fun, fun Hamburg...?

00:12:22.343 --> 00:12:24.491
zaynen mir ale lebn geblibn.

00:12:24.149 --> 00:12:26.420
ay- ale lebn geblibn?.

