iz, zaynen mir aroys oyfn mist,

00:13:49.060 --> 00:13:52.882
hobn mir gekha-, s'iz geven dortn, az zey flegn sheyln far di daytshn,

00:13:52.882 --> 00:13:55.520
 di kartofl flegn zey opsheyln,

00:13:55.527 --> 00:13:59.288
iz d⟨i⟩ mist... hot eyne gearbet in kikh, hot zi undz gezogt

