 zey hobn gehat a bisl mer esn, vayl ⟨zey zaynen gev-⟩ ober zey hobn undz nit, ⟨zey⟩ zaynen geven fayn tsu undz, ye. zey zaynen nit, di meydlekh zaynen geven fayn tsu undz, un mir zaynen ale bafrayt gevorn.

