m'iz baf- m'hot ⟨z-⟩ aro⟨yf⟩geleygt

00:15:25.386 --> 00:15:27.256
broyt, marmelad,

00:15:27.256 --> 00:15:31.534
tsib-... vos s'iz dortn geven. m'iz gegangen un di d- Englender hobn undz nit gelozn.

00:15:31.534 --> 00:15:33.176
mir hobn nit farshtanen.

00:15:32.503 --> 00:15:33.503
⟨s-⟩...

00:15:33.385 --> 00:15:38.154
vayle m'iz geven oysgedart, oysge- m'hot nit getort esn.

00:15:38.295 --> 00:15:44.004
m'hot gedarft onheybn azoy, zey hobn undz gege- un az zey hobn undz oykh nit gegebn bald azoy fil, hot men zey

00:15:44.004 --> 00:15:47.455
gesholtn un geshrien, punkt vi di daytshn. un az zey hobn nit gelozn undz...

00:15:47.455 --> 00:15:49.590
ober m'hot nit gekukt, m'iz gegangen

00:15:49.590 --> 00:15:56.008
shik- azoy vi shikere mentshn, un mentshn zaynen gefaln krank, vayle zey zaynen geven krank, ye.

00:15:56.031 --> 00:16:01.428
un s'iz gekumen bald der Royter Kreyts un tsugenumen a sakh in di shpiteler, vayle s'iz dokh geven

00:16:01.428 --> 00:16:03.652
TYPHUS kranke un dos o.

00:16:04.047 --> 00:16:11.537
un me hot getantst un geshprungen un geshprungen krankerheyt un me hot gehulyet un m'iz geven azoy freylekh.

00:16:11.537 --> 00:16:12.337
un

00:16:12.337 --> 00:16:14.449
nakher iz gekumen

00:16:14.449 --> 00:16:19.727
a bafel az me zol aroys fun dem shmu- un in di lagern dortn iz gelegn F-

00:16:19.727 --> 00:16:24.403
MOUNTAIN FURS vos zey hobn ongeshlept fun ale mentshn vos zaynen gekumen,

00:16:24.403 --> 00:16:31.609
un p- ge- farpakt avektsufirn far zey, far di daytshn. ober in lager hobn zey dos alts, fun azoy fil mentshn geven.

00:16:31.609 --> 00:16:33.996
gantse magazinen iz geven

00:16:33.996 --> 00:16:43.764
mit glezer un mit FUR COATS un mit kold- un di beste zakhn, vos zey hobn dos far zikh alts, zey zoln dos, far zikh nemen.

00:16:44.158 --> 00:16:48.269
iz, m'hot gekhapt, ongeton zikh, ober

00:16:48.343 --> 00:16:50.339
me hot gezogt az

00:16:50.339 --> 00:16:54.474
me vet undz alemen durkhloyzn. dos heyst, mit aza vaysn POWDER.

00:16:54.474 --> 00:16:56.994
m'hot zikh alts oysge- gedarft oyston.

00:16:55.768 --> 00:16:57.821
mit a vaysn, a puder?

00:16:57.304 --> 00:16:58.541
a puder,

00:16:58.221 --> 00:16:58.691
⟨⟩...

00:16:58.541 --> 00:16:59.503
vayle

00:16:59.503 --> 00:17:02.635
di tifus un MAYBE layz un MAYBE vos.

00:17:02.635 --> 00:17:07.136
un m'hot undz alemen durkh- azoy durkhgepudert. s'iz avek efsher a vokh tsvey.

00:17:05.817 --> 00:17:08.262
⟨⟩, ver hot dos geton?,

00:17:07.294 --> 00:17:10.173
di Englender. dos iz geven a...

00:17:08.262 --> 00:17:11.473
englishe... menershe soldatn tsi vayber?

00:17:11.878 --> 00:17:12.471
n-

00:17:12.644 --> 00:17:13.644
⟨,⟩

00:17:14.060 --> 00:17:17.289
mit di kleydl. iz, ikh gedenk, ye, hot men undz...

00:17:14.989 --> 00:17:18.324
oh, mit di kley- oh. oh, oh, s'iz geven iber di kleyder?

00:17:17.289 --> 00:17:20.293
iber di, ye. hot men undz azoy iberge-...

00:17:20.293 --> 00:17:22.829
un me hot undz avekgefirt

00:17:22.869 --> 00:17:28.736
in di kosharn, do vu s'zaynen di daytshn geshtanen, d⟨i s-⟩ militer. der lager iz dokh geven

00:17:28.962 --> 00:17:30.030
toyte,

00:17:30.030 --> 00:17:32.855
un hiltserne barakn alts,

00:17:32.855 --> 00:17:36.974
un ongemakht un altsding; d-, s'iz dokh geven a toyte⟨r⟩ lager.

00:17:36.974 --> 00:17:42.981
hot men undz aribergefirt in militerishe, in sheyne ROOMkes, mit alts.

00:17:42.981 --> 00:17:45.006
dan zaynen mir ale ariber...

00:17:45.006 --> 00:17:47.040
nokhn antloyzn un alts

00:17:47.040 --> 00:17:51.551
iz men ariber, un dortn hobn mir shoyn gekrogn fun di UNRRA

00:17:51.793 --> 00:17:55.466
esn. s'iz geven a kikh, un me fleg geb-

00:17:54.072 --> 00:17:55.871
⟨,⟩ vo- vos heyst UNRRA?

00:17:56.123 --> 00:18:01.071
 der JOINT, der UNRRA, hot dos geheysn. Amerikaner,

00:17:59.443 --> 00:18:02.283
⟨s-⟩ an organizatsye?

00:18:01.071 --> 00:18:03.096
azoy v- ye, organizatsyes.

00:18:03.096 --> 00:18:08.403
 azoy vi do, Amerika- az m'iz gekumen, hot geholfn der HIAS, der dos;

00:18:08.403 --> 00:18:11.194
dortn iz geven di UNRRA, hot men dos gerufn.

00:18:11.217 --> 00:18:18.731
 yidishe organiz- un MAYBE fun Amerike, un m'hot geshikt peklekh un m'hot undz gegebn, un MAYBE der Royter Kreyts.

00:18:18.731 --> 00:18:21.251
un m'hot undz shoyn gegebn esn.

00:18:19.924 --> 00:18:20.711
vu...

00:18:21.055 --> 00:18:23.884
un vu zayt ir geshlofn oyf der ershter nakht,

00:18:24.143 --> 00:18:25.824
nokh der bafrayung?

00:18:24.193 --> 00:18:25.206
nokh di ba-...?

00:18:25.206 --> 00:18:35.732
iz, oh, dortn iz men gelegn oyf di pritshn. nokh di bafrayung iz men nokh alts, ⟨iz men⟩ nokh geven efsher dray vokhn, tsvey, tsvey vokhn iz men nokh alts geven in dem shmutsikn lager,

00:18:35.732 --> 00:18:37.319
bizkl,...

00:18:37.319 --> 00:18:42.699
nakher hot men undz, durkhge- "antloyzt," heyst dos. me hot undz,

00:18:43.060 --> 00:18:44.484
 a disinfektsye.

00:18:43.971 --> 00:18:48.858
iz dos nisht geven a groyse sakone tsu blaybn dort mit di, mit di bergn?

00:18:44.484 --> 00:18:45.484
a di-...

00:18:47.309 --> 00:18:51.055
 ir't nit gehat keyn eytse! dos iz, ⟨, he, me...⟩

00:18:51.055 --> 00:18:56.995
 me hot undz a disinfektsye gemakht, mit altsding. hot men undz aribergeshikt in di barakn,

00:18:56.995 --> 00:19:00.671
 do vu di soldatn zaynen geven.

00:19:00.778 --> 00:19:03.725
un dervayle hobn mir gehat aza nekome:

00:19:03.782 --> 00:19:11.909
 di daytshn, di daytshn vos zaynen geven in lager hobn gedarft oyfklaybn ale toyte fun di gantse lager

00:19:11.983 --> 00:19:13.833
un aroyfleygn oyf

00:19:13.907 --> 00:19:15.149
oytos.

00:19:15.409 --> 00:19:19.993
un, zey zaynen shoyn geven on di HAT, un ⟨ir⟩ veyst dokh, ⟨azoy, nor⟩ dem...

00:19:20.151 --> 00:19:30.846
un, u- un di toyte zaynen gelegn, do⟨rt⟩ gelegn f- mistome far monatn. iz geg- ge- zet oys, s'iz geven aza shl⟨yuz⟩, aza, azoy vi a vaser, aza glitshiker,

00:19:30.846 --> 00:19:32.717
azoy vi fleysh, ligt v⟨UNK⟩...

00:19:32.841 --> 00:19:34.146
iz, zet oyset,

00:19:34.146 --> 00:19:37.256
⟨ho-⟩ vayl ikh hob gezen vi zey hobn zikh azoy gevisht.

00:19:37.414 --> 00:19:42.760
un, un mir zaynen geshtanen un gekukt un m'hot gekhapt shteyner un gevorfn oyf zey,

00:19:42.760 --> 00:19:45.558
ober di Englender hobn undz oykh nit tsugelozn.

00:19:46.122 --> 00:19:54.472
un, un di eyntsike nekome: mir zaynen geshtanen un geshrien oyf zey un gevorfn shteyner, un di nekome iz geven groys. un zey hobn

00:19:54.472 --> 00:19:57.104
ongeleygt gantse oytos mit di toyte,

00:19:57.104 --> 00:20:00.679
un s'iz geven oysgegrobene griber, groyse griber,

00:20:00.837 --> 00:20:07.328
un m'hot ale dortn... oder dortn hostu ale NATIONS; me veys nit ver s'iz a yid un ver s'iz a goy, vayle

00:20:07.384 --> 00:20:09.988
s'iz gelegn ongeleygt gantse, ye.

00:20:09.988 --> 00:20:17.299
un mit, un mener un froyen, iz alts lign in, e- etlekhe griber iz dortn do.

00:20:17.299 --> 00:20:19.337
nor dos iz geven undzer nekome,

00:20:19.337 --> 00:20:20.540
az zey hobn,

00:20:20.597 --> 00:20:21.480
,

00:20:21.480 --> 00:20:26.778
a nekome undzer tsar, ober di nekome az zey, zaynen geven gefangene, ye.

00:20:26.778 --> 00:20:29.922
un zey hobn opgeCLEANt di lagern fun ale toyte.

00:20:30.030 --> 00:20:34.462
un m'hot zey arestirt, un, ikh veys vos m'hot mit zey geton.

00:20:34.536 --> 00:20:42.917
un nakher hot men undz arayngeshikt in di lagern vu zey zaynen geshtanen, in di geboyte militerishe hayzer, in Bergen-Belzen, ye.

00:20:43.041 --> 00:20:50.122
bizkl, nakher, yederer hot zikh shoyn, gekumen tsu zikh un, yederer hot zikh shoyn gezukht,

00:20:50.179 --> 00:20:54.708
 aroystsugeyn. nakher, iz men aroys;

00:20:55.292 --> 00:20:58.559
efsher a dray-fir vokhn iz men aroys shoyn in shtot.

00:20:58.785 --> 00:21:02.930
vayle der lager iz nokh alts geven farshpart; m'hot undz ⟨nokh⟩ nit gelozn aroysgeyn.

00:21:02.987 --> 00:21:04.140
andere,

00:21:04.140 --> 00:21:14.642
 zaynen gegangen, vos zey hobn gerabevet bay di d-, zey hobn tseharget di daytshn nokh di krig, alts. ⟨mi- undz⟩ hot men nit aroysgelozn. iz shoyn geven efsher dray-fir vokhn,

00:21:14.648 --> 00:21:17.884
hobn mir shoyn gornit,... nor ven mir zaynen aroys,

00:21:17.884 --> 00:21:22.314
iz geven a sakh leydike daytshishe hayzer. far vos? zey hobn moyre gehat,

00:21:22.314 --> 00:21:23.673
az di katsetler...

00:21:23.673 --> 00:21:28.567
zey zaynen dokh a- arum di lagern gevoynt, hobn zey dokh moyre gehat az m'vet zey efsher epes ton.

00:21:28.567 --> 00:21:36.393
iz geven, a bisl leydike hayzer, ober, mir hobn zey gornit gekent ton, vayle s'iz geven der lager nokh alts farshpart.

00:21:35.961 --> 00:21:39.735
mit, mit vemen zayt ir gegangen? mit etlekhe khaveyrim?

00:21:39.066 --> 00:21:43.015
etl- khavertes, meydlekh. nakher iz men aroys, nakher iz men,

00:21:43.015 --> 00:21:44.286
 hot men gevart;

00:21:44.286 --> 00:21:49.635
iz gekumen, shpeter zaynen gekumen fun andere lagern, a mol a bruder fun an ander lager,

00:21:49.635 --> 00:21:53.094
un s'iz geven... un m'hot zikh arumgekhapt az s'iz gekumen ver

00:21:53.094 --> 00:22:01.503
vos iz lebn geblibn. oy, hot men zikh arumgekhapt un geveynt un gefreyt zikh az s'iz, az s'iz ver lebn geblibn, ⟨iz⟩ gekumen fun andere lagern.

00:22:01.510 --> 00:22:06.662
un nakher, iz men gegangen shoyn, iz men shoyn fray geven.

00:22:06.662 --> 00:22:07.436
ye.

00:22:06.775 --> 00:22:08.383
vu hot,

00:22:08.383 --> 00:22:12.995
 vos hot ir geton kedey tsu gefinen, ⟨⟩, mishpokhe, kroyvim, epes?

00:22:12.057 --> 00:22:21.571
ikh veys az ikh hob nit gehat. kh'veys, mayn tatn hot men tsugenumen, mayn bruder hot men oykhet, un mayn shvester hot men tsugenumen, mayn mame v- hob ikh gevust, un mayn bruderl, hob ikh gevust az ikh hob keynem nit.

00:22:21.571 --> 00:22:23.697
un a kuzinke iz geven mit mir.

00:22:23.697 --> 00:22:26.076
zi iz yetst in Yisroel. zi iz geven ⟨in⟩ eynem...

00:22:26.076 --> 00:22:29.819
un dos iz di eyntsike, ye. az m'hot nit gehat, ye.

00:22:29.033 --> 00:22:32.047
 vos, vi heyst di kuzinke vos iz geven mit aykh?

00:22:31.800 --> 00:22:32.924
Merele.

00:22:32.610 --> 00:22:33.633
Merele?

00:22:32.948 --> 00:22:33.769
z- ye.

00:22:33.995 --> 00:22:35.425
un, d-...

00:22:34.550 --> 00:22:36.671
zi iz geven tsvishn di finef hundert?

00:22:35.867 --> 00:22:37.163
ye. ye.

00:22:36.866 --> 00:22:37.340
⟨ah⟩.

00:22:37.163 --> 00:22:39.619
un dos iz, di...

00:22:39.619 --> 00:22:42.538
un m- un a tante hob ikh., zi, zi iz geven

00:22:42.538 --> 00:22:46.053
fun di likvidatsye fun yidishe g-, fun di Vilner geto.

00:22:46.397 --> 00:22:50.908
zi iz geven fun di letste, fun di likvidatsye. zi iz geven in,

00:22:50.987 --> 00:22:55.790
in Letland. zey hot men avekgefirt, di likvidatsye UNK, a sakh nokh AUSCHWITZ,

00:22:56.100 --> 00:22:57.928
un a sakh nokh Letland.

00:22:57.928 --> 00:23:03.678
zi iz geven in Letland. un ir kind iz dos geven vos m'hot tsugenumen dan, vos kh'hob aykh gezogt, zibn-akht monat.

00:23:03.694 --> 00:23:04.340
ye.

00:23:04.340 --> 00:23:06.455
un zi iz bafrayt gevorn, ye.

00:23:06.671 --> 00:23:07.206
ye.

00:23:06.725 --> 00:23:07.806
hot ir ge-

00:23:07.828 --> 00:23:10.252
gezukht tantes un...?

00:23:09.280 --> 00:23:11.892
me hot gezukht, me hot gezukht, ober...

